video.title: Sofia the First
video.synopsis: When her commoner mother marries the king, average-girl Sofia finds that being a real princess isn't all it's cracked up to be.

episodes.synopsis: Sofia and her family go to the Flying Royal Derby. The little princess is excited to see the event and even decides to participate.
episodes.title: Just One of the Princes

episodes.synopsis: It's Sofia's first royal slumber party and Amber invites the other princesses to the event. Sofia invites her friends from town.
episodes.title: The Big Sleepover

episodes.synopsis: Sofia enters the cave where the Trolls live. King Roland tells her that the Trolls can never leave their caves.
episodes.title: Let the Good Times Troll

episodes.synopsis: Sofia has a big test coming up in her spellcasting classes, but she can't seem to get the spell down, so she asks Cedric for help.
episodes.title: Cedric's Apprentice

episodes.synopsis: The Golden Wing Circus returns to Enchancia and the kids want to see it. But James breaks a window playing ball in the castle.
episodes.title: A Royal Mess

episodes.synopsis: The kids at school are assigned the task of designing the castle of their dreams, but it's a group project and the teachers select the partners.
episodes.title: The Shy Princess

episodes.synopsis: Sofia enters Clover in the Village Faire pet contest and learns an important lesson in friendship after inadvertently hurting his feelings.
episodes.title: Blue Ribbon Bunny

episodes.synopsis: It's the day of the big princess test. Everyone gets ready with their best dresses. Mrs. Higgins asks for help, but everyone's too busy to help her.
episodes.title: The Princess Test

episodes.synopsis: Baileywick's brother Nigel comes to visit for his birthday. The King gives him the day off, but every time they try to leave, someone asks for help.
episodes.title: Baileywick's Day Off

episodes.synopsis: The Kingdoms of Wei-Ling, Khaldoun and Enchancia meet to celebrate a royal picnic and a day of outdoor games. James asks Sofia to be his teammate.
episodes.title: Tri-Kingdom Picnic

episodes.synopsis: It's Jade's birthday and she prepares a party and the whole town's invited, except Lucinda, the witch, who treats everyone badly.
episodes.title: The Little Witch

episodes.synopsis: Everyone goes to the land of Tangu to visit Zandar. He's getting ready to throw a big party with magic carpets.
episodes.title: Two to Tangu

episodes.synopsis: Clover thinks Sofia doesn't have time for him, so he decides to go to a wizard who can turn him into a magic rabbit.
episodes.title: Finding Clover

episodes.synopsis: Sofia and Amber take a jewel for the royal ball. One of the griffins, the creatures who guard the jewels, escapes.
episodes.title: The Amulet of Avalor

episodes.synopsis: Sofia wants to go on a hike with her Buttercup troop, but King Roland insists on sending Baileywick, the castle steward, to keep Sofia safe.
episodes.title: The Buttercups

episodes.synopsis: A new fairy teacher, Miss Nettle, who was once the apprentice of Flora, Fauna and Merryweather, arrives at Royal Prep to be a teacher for the after-school gardening club.
episodes.title: Make Way for Miss Nettle

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia brags about being chosen to sing the Enchancian anthem, her amulet puts a curse on her, which she must learn to undo.
episodes.title: The Amulet and the Anthem

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia is selected to host a Royal Prep tea party, Amber encourages her to "think big" to impress the princes and princesses.
episodes.title: Tea for Too Many

episodes.synopsis: The students at Royal Prep must make their own costumes for this year's All Hallows' Eve costume contest.
episodes.title: Princess Butterfly

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia reluctantly agrees to help her seemingly dotty Aunt Tilly bake an apple pie, she thinks she's in for a boring day.
episodes.title: Great Aunt-Venture

episodes.synopsis: King Roland finds an enchanted mirror in the castle attic and accidentally makes a wish for a simple life as a village baker.
episodes.title: The Baker King

episodes.synopsis: During her family vacation on a floating palace, Sofia arrives at a special cove and befriends a curious young mermaid.
episodes.title: The Floating Palace: Pt. 1

episodes.synopsis: Sofia tries to find a way to convince her parents to move the floating palace to save the mermaid kingdom.
episodes.title: The Floating Palace: Pt. 2

episodes.synopsis: When a snowstorm prevents King Roland from returning home in time for the holidays, Sofia leads her family on a brave expedition to find him.
episodes.title: Holiday in Enchancia

episodes.synopsis: Sofia invites Jade and Ruby, her village friends, to join her and her sister, Amber, in the Flylight Pageant, an annual parade of flying coaches.
episodes.title: Four's a Crowd

episodes.synopsis: Amber doesn't want to share her birthday with James anymore, so she asks Cedric to cast a spell giving them different birthdays.
episodes.title: Two Princesses and a Baby

episodes.synopsis: When the evil fairy, Miss Nettle, tries to steal her amulet during the Enchanted Feast, Sofia gets some help from Snow White.
episodes.title: The Enchanted Feast

episodes.synopsis: When an injury keeps James from competing in the flying derby championship, Sofia must team up with Prince Hugo.
episodes.title: The Flying Crown

episodes.synopsis: Sofia doesn't want to share her mother with her siblings at a Mother's Day picnic and asks Lucinda to cast a spell giving the two of them time alone.
episodes.title: Mom's the Word

episodes.synopsis: Sofia gets to meet her hero, Sir Bartleby, who doesn't speak because of his unusual voice, and introduces him to her Aunt Tilly.
episodes.title: The Silent Knight

episodes.synopsis: As the Enchanted Science Fair nears, Sofia and her classmates pair up to find magical objects atop a mountain, a quest that tests their friendship.
episodes.title: Enchanted Science Fair

episodes.synopsis: With his parents away, James is made king for the day, but things get out of hand when he refuses to take the job seriously.
episodes.title: King for a Day

episodes.synopsis: A jealous Amber makes a wish that Roland becomes allergic to Sofia but she doesn't mean to turn Sofia into a cat!
episodes.title: When You Wish upon a Well

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia meets Gwen, a young kitchen maid with a talent for inventing, she encourages her to follow her creative dreams.
episodes.title: Gizmo Gwen

episodes.synopsis: Sofia uses a spell to make a double of herself so she can be in two places at once, but the copy ends up causing trouble at the Highland Hootenanny.
episodes.title: Sofia the Second

episodes.synopsis: Sofia joins Cedric for a visit to a sorcerers' retirement home, where he hopes to earn his father's respect and his family's magic wand.
episodes.title: Mystic Meadows

episodes.synopsis: When James and Prince Jin become trapped in the kingdom of Wei-Ling, Sofia, Amber and Jun team up with Mulan to rescue them.
episodes.title: Princesses to the Rescue!

episodes.synopsis: A ghost is scaring everyone away from Sofia's big Halloween bash, but she soon discovers that he just wants to host a party of his own.
episodes.title: Ghostly Gala

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia and Hildegard become trapped inside a magic painting, Hildegard's know-it-all attitude complicates their escape.
episodes.title: The Princess Stays in the Picture

episodes.synopsis: Two princesses arrive in Enchancia, each claiming to own an emerald key that Sofia found. Which is the real princess, and which the imposter?
episodes.title: The Emerald Key

episodes.synopsis: Sofia and her classmates bring their pets to school, where they get "scrambled" during an experiment in sorcery class.
episodes.title: Scrambled Pets

episodes.synopsis: A new steward casts a spell on Baileywick, hoping to steal his job. But Sofia helps to make sure her friend doesn't fall into the trap.
episodes.title: Baileywhoops

episodes.synopsis: Jealous of Sofia's magic amulet, Amber steals it for herself, a deed that unleashes the wicked Princess Ivy who wants to take over Enchancia.
episodes.title: The Curse of Princess Ivy: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: While evil Princess Ivy tries to destroy the amulet, Amber turns to Sofia and Rapunzel for help defeating Ivy and saving Enchancia.
episodes.title: The Curse of Princess Ivy: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: While looking for the perfect Wassailia gift for Cedric, Sofia meets a faun in the woods who's suffering from a terrible curse.
episodes.title: Winter's Gift

episodes.synopsis: Crackle would love to sing in the Leafsong Festival but fears that she'll have to give up her fire-breathing ability to participate.
episodes.title: The Leafsong Festival

episodes.synopsis: When Cedric steps in to teach Sofia's sorcery class, a group of his former students play a series of pranks that threatens to get out of hand.
episodes.title: Substitute Cedric

episodes.synopsis: After water floods his home, Clover moves in with Sofia. The princess is delighted, at least until Clover proves how untidy he can be.
episodes.title: Clover Time

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to win a big race, Ruby asks fairy godmother Tizzy to lend a hand. But the fairy's super-enthusiastic help makes Ruby sorry she ever asked.
episodes.title: In a Tizzy

episodes.synopsis: When the villagers take on the royal court in a game of dazzleball, Sofia must choose whose team to join -- her friends' or her family's.
episodes.title: A Tale of Two Teams

episodes.synopsis: Sofia's amulet magically lets her become tiny in order to save three sprites. But when she misbehaves, the amulet won't let her return to normal size.
episodes.title: The Littlest Princess

episodes.synopsis: Amber joins a troop of Butternut scouts, but a grungy overnight trip proves challenging for the princess who prefers to remain pristine.
episodes.title: Buttercup Amber

episodes.synopsis: Sofia tries to do a good deed to prove that the royal family cares about the villagers, but a local hero's jealous follower thwarts her efforts.
episodes.title: Carol of the Arrow

episodes.synopsis: Though Sofia encourages her to try out for the school musical, gifted singer Clio hesitates because she's afraid her friend Hildegard will disapprove.
episodes.title: Sidekick Clio

episodes.synopsis: It's up to Sofia and her royal siblings to save the day when a young wizard lures Minimus and Enchancia's other flying horses away with a magic lute.
episodes.title: Minimus Is Missing

episodes.synopsis: Sofia's friend Prince Hugo loves to ice dance, but he's afraid of what his father, King Garrick, will think. Can Sofia help her pal follow his heart?
episodes.title: Lord of the Rink

episodes.synopsis: When the royal family visits Merroway Cove, Oona's brash friend Fluke becomes jealous of Sofia and all the attention she receives.
episodes.title: Cool Hand Fluke

episodes.synopsis: When Cedric secretly gets ahold of Sofia's amulet, he wants to use it for his own gain. But the amulet doesn't take kindly to thieves.
episodes.title: Cedric Be Good

episodes.synopsis: Princess Zooey enrolls at Royal Prep and starts a Princess Adventure Club. But things get complicated when Princess Amber starts a club of her own.
episodes.title: Princess Adventure Club

episodes.synopsis: When Aunt Tilly leaves Sofia in charge of her magical manor house, the young princess finds herself battling a trio of pesky gargoyles.
episodes.title: Minding the Manor

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia discovers a secret library in the castle, she finds that many of the books are unfinished -- and it's up to her to give them happy endings.
episodes.title: The Secret Library

episodes.synopsis: While traveling to Tangu, Sofia accidentally unleashes a genie who sets out to grant as many wishes as possible, no matter the consequences.
episodes.title: New Genie on the Block

episodes.synopsis: When an unfriendly fliegel named Grotta starts bullying Gnarly the troll, it's up to Sofia to help her friend stick up for himself.
episodes.title: The Fliegel Has Landed

episodes.synopsis: Princess Kari is naturally great at everything -- except for ballet. Sofia tries to help her friend remember that having fun is what's most important.
episodes.title: The Princess Ballet

episodes.synopsis: Not wanting to move, Princess Vivian asks the mischievous Wee Sprites to trick her parents by making it appear like her new castle is haunted.
episodes.title: All the Sprite Moves

episodes.synopsis: Sofia is delighted to discover the enchanted land of Elvenmoor, but she soon realizes that she could get stuck there forever.
episodes.title: Sofia in Elevenmoor

episodes.synopsis: Sofia visits her friend Lani, who wants to prove her leadership on a special quest. But Lani's temper has a way of stirring up trouble.
episodes.title: Stormy Lani

episodes.synopsis: After learning that Miss Nettle is taking snowdrops from Freezenburg, Sofia sets out to stop the stealing with some help from a surprising ally.
episodes.title: The Secret Library: Olaf and the Tale of Miss Nettle

episodes.synopsis: Sofia, Cedric and his niece, Calista, enjoy a visit to Merlin the wizard. But when Calista swipes Merlin's wand, things get dangerous.
episodes.title: Gone with the Wand

episodes.synopsis: Sofia and Vivian take in a cute little dragon they find while picking berries, but Crackle soon discovers that their new friend is a cunning thief.
episodes.title: Bad Little Dragon

episodes.synopsis: While visiting town, Clover meets a rabbit that looks just like him. When the two accidentally switch places, Clover must find his own way home.
episodes.title: Bunny Swap

episodes.synopsis: While spying on people with her telescope, Amber thinks she spots a mystical creature that could pose a danger to her mother.
episodes.title: Her Royal Spyness

episodes.synopsis: When the Flying Starwings come to perform at the castle, Sofia tries to help their son, Minimus, gain the courage to do a stunt in their show.
episodes.title: Best in Air Show

episodes.synopsis: Sofia and the princesses go on a special Dads and Daughters Day adventure, but Sofia worries she doesn't belong because Roland is her stepfather.
episodes.title: Dads and Daughters Day

episodes.synopsis: Sofia goes to the secret library to read about Sir Oliver, the Noble Knight, but when she and Minimus fly into the story, the plot thickens.
episodes.title: The Secret Library: The Tale of the Noble Knight

episodes.synopsis: In Wei Ling, Sofia wants to help Princess Jun cure her cold in time for the kite festival and sets out to learn if the old cures are better than new.
episodes.title: The Bamboo Kite

episodes.synopsis: The amulet sends Sofia to Isleworth to help Charlotte, a fellow princess who's miserable since being turned into a beast by an enchantress's curse.
episodes.title: Beauty Is the Beast

episodes.synopsis: Lucinda invites Sofia to her Cauldronation party, where she'll be made a true midnight witch, if Sofia can stop two rival witches from ruining things.
episodes.title: Cauldronation Day

episodes.synopsis: Sofia, James and Amber head to their first summer camp, where Amber has a hard time adjusting, and homesick James plots an escape with a new friend.
episodes.title: Camp Wilderwood

episodes.synopsis: Miranda's sad that the family is too busy to spend quality time together, so Sofia suggests a family vacation, but things don't go exactly as planned.
episodes.title: Royal Vacation

episodes.synopsis: Sofia goes to the library for the truth about the amulet and learns that Princess Elena of Avalor was locked inside it trying to save her people.
episodes.title: Elena and the Secret of Avalor: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Sofia gets help from new friends in Avalor and finally frees Elena, but that's only the first step in saving the kingdom from the sorceress Shuriki.
episodes.title: Elena and the Secret of Avalor: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Shuriki's jailed Sofia's family and trapped Elena's in a painting. But with help from the Avalor people -- and some magic -- they may have a chance.
episodes.title: Elena and the Secret of Avalor: Part 3

episodes.synopsis: When the amulet starts to change, Sofia consults with Cedric, who suggests they visit his old school, Hexley Hall, where things have also changed.
episodes.title: Hexley Hall

episodes.synopsis: The Royal Prep band impresses at a music competition, thanks to Vivian's magical playing, which inspires a famed musician to try to steal her talent.
episodes.title: The Princess Prodigy

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia, James and Amber return to school, they're promoted to the Majestic class but find professor Pecullian's methods a bit peculiar.
episodes.title: One for the Books

episodes.synopsis: After a secret meeting with sorcerers, Cedric must choose between taking the throne or keeping his friendship with Sofia.
episodes.title: Day of the Sorcerers

episodes.synopsis: Sofia embarks on a risky mission to find an enchanted and highly sought-after flame but James makes the task more difficult.
episodes.title: The Secret Library: Tale of the Eternal Torch

episodes.synopsis: For the Festival of Plenty, Sofia receives the honor of wearing the Crown of Blossoms as Clover gets stingy with his veggies and gnomes eye the crown.
episodes.title: The Crown of Blossoms

episodes.synopsis: When Kazeem is accused of causing chaos in Tangu, Sofia goes to great lengths to prove his innocence.
episodes.title: Pin the Blame on the Genie

episodes.synopsis: Amber demands Sofia help her stop an evil Crystalmaster from covering the Isles in magic crystals -- but secretly wants to secure an amulet of her own.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Amber, Sofia and Prisma journey through the Isles, where Amber gets a bitter taste of queendom and Prisma's plan becomes crystal clear.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Together, Sofia and Amber search for a magical stone that will shatter an evil scheme to destroy inhabitants of the Isles.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: Part 3

episodes.synopsis: Sofia meets the feisty Crystal Fairy set to train and protect her. Later, she tackles her first assignment at the Isle of Forever Frost.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: The Princess and the Protector

episodes.synopsis: When Crackle has no one to attend the Roast 'n' Toast celebration with, Sofia works her magic to accompany her. Sir Oliver plots to ruin the event.
episodes.title: The Royal Dragon

episodes.synopsis: For the next step in becoming a protector, Sofia must find a magical horse. When she chooses the unicorn Skye to help her, Minimus feels left out.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: The Mare of the Mist

episodes.synopsis: When Cedric's sister moves to Enchancia Castle, a rift forms between the two siblings. Sofia and Calista use a magical mirror to see what caused it.
episodes.title: Through the Looking Back Glass

episodes.synopsis: At Royal Prep's School Swap Day, Amber tries not to stumble in Dunwiddie while Sofia finds a photo that makes her believe Jade is a royal.
episodes.title: Princess Jade

episodes.synopsis: When her amulet summons her to help a princess in need, Sofia finds herself face to face with an old enemy.
episodes.title: Ivy's True Colors

episodes.synopsis: As Halloween falls over Enchancia, Sofia goes trick-or-treating with her witch friends who complain that little Calista is ruining the holiday spirit.
episodes.title: Too Cute to Spook

episodes.synopsis: When Sofia, Amber and Miranda set sail to see a meteor shower, they help a group of sailors looking for treasure and are put in danger themselves.
episodes.title: Pirated Away

episodes.synopsis: As Prisma sets her sights on the Wicked Nine to regain her power, Sofia and Chrysta head to Wei-Ling to protect a magical jewel.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: The Falcon's Eye

episodes.synopsis: Prisma hunts for another precious object from the Wicked Nine hidden inside Royal Prep, where a guest teacher dazzles Sofia and her classmates.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: The Great Pretender

episodes.synopsis: When Chrysta pitches in for last-minute Protector duties during the holiday of Wassailia, Sofia works on a special celebration for Chrysta.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: A Very Mystic Wassailia

episodes.synopsis: After a series of mishaps, Sofia makes a wish to relive her birthday trouble-free -- until a spell has her stuck in a time loop.
episodes.title: The Birthday Wish

episodes.synopsis: When Cedric is accused of stealing the Crown of Queen Grimhilde, he works overtime to capture the culprit and regain the king's trust.
episodes.title: In Cedric We Trust

episodes.synopsis: Things go awry when Clover falsely assumes the role of Protector for the Hoodwinks while Sofia heads off for more training.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: A Hero for the Hoodwinks

episodes.synopsis: Sofia and Chrysta visit the Fairy Forest, where they go undercover to guard the magic of the Pixie Cup blossom.
episodes.title: The Mystic Isles: Undercover Fairies

episodes.synopsis: As excitement for Aunt Tilly's and Sir Bartleby's wedding stirs, the royal family clashes over the next ruler of Enchancia.
episodes.title: A Royal Wedding

episodes.synopsis: Sofia faces a big decision about her future school while Desmond second-guesses his dreams of becoming a knight.
episodes.title: The Royal School Fair

episodes.synopsis: During a trip to recover an ancient treasure, the Princess Adventure Club relies on all of their senses to navigate a series of dangerous booby traps.
episodes.title: The Lost Pyramid

episodes.synopsis: When Princess Oona conjures a wild sea twister, her mother and Sofia step in to stop the rampaging water disaster.
episodes.title: Return to Merroway Cove

episodes.synopsis: When their parents leave them in charge, Sofia, Amber and James attempt to make peace between two fighting elves.
episodes.title: The Elf Situation

episodes.synopsis: In the finale, Sofia, Amber and James prepare to graduate from Royal Prep Academy amid threats from an evil sorceress named Vor.
episodes.title: Forever Royal, Part I

episodes.synopsis: As Sofia's graduation party prep begins in the castle, Vor seeks revenge on the Protectors and the Kingdom of Enchancia.
episodes.title: Forever Royal, Part II

episodes.synopsis: When Vor casts a mind-control spell over the royal family, Sofia must face her biggest challenge yet and save the people of Enchancia.
episodes.title: Forever Royal, Part III
